                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman X R</hi> 33). On 15th October, the prisoner was given into my custody by the last witness, and I received this bad shilling from him—I searched the prisoner, and found a good shilling—he was charged at the Police Court, remanded, and discharged.</p>
               <p>
